other_tests.findings: Lower Thorax: Trace left pleural effusion and bibasilar atelectasis. Liver: Unremarkable with trace perihepatic free fluid. Biliary: No biliary duct dilatation. Gallbladder: Unremarkable. No choledocholithiasis. Pancreas: Peripancreatic soft tissue, mild edema within the pancreatic head and body with decreased intrinsic parenchymal T1 hyperintensity. Homogeneous enhancement of the pancreas noted. No mass demonstrated. A pancreatic duct divisum variant noted.
